title: Ondara - three song performances for The Current (2020)
description:
Back in October 2020, Ondara connected with The Current to perform three songs from Folk N' Roll Volume 1: Tales Of America, his album from that year. Watch those performances in the video above.

SONGS PERFORMED
0:00 "Pulled Out of the Market"
3:55 "Lockdown on Date Night Tuesday"
8:55 "Pyramid Justice"
